        <h3 class="wiki-nav-item pb-2" id="performance-nvidia">
            Poor performance with NVIDIA
        </h3>
        <div class="ms-3">
            <ol>
                <li>Disable <code>Force full composition pipeline</code> in the NVIDIA settings panel.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

